    <div class="col6        ">
        
                
                                                                                                <p>Our graduates are career-ready from day one. We make this happen by introducing hands-on learning early, guided by faculty who have practiced in the field. From healthcare simulation labs to audio engineering studios, our students participate in real-world scenarios, training them for future careers.</p>
<p>Take the first step toward an exceptional educational journey by exploring the opportunities at Husson University. Our Admissions and Financial Aid team is ready to assist you throughout the process and help you embark on a path of growth, discovery, and success. Join us and discover your potential as a Husson Eagle!</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p><a class="ctaButton" href="https://admissions.husson.edu/register/requestinformation" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Request Info</a> <a class="ctaButton" href="https://admissions.husson.edu/apply/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Apply Now</a></p>
                            
                                                
                                        
